children.content: Now it's time for the men and boys from the NRL. Here's the list:
It's the Panthers youngster who gets the nod!
That's a bit of a surprise - I think plenty were tipping Jahream Bula.
He thanks the coaching staff and "the boys" for giving him the confidence.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: It's Petero Civoniceva who will present this award. Here's the NRLW nominees: Annessa Biddle (Sharks) China Polata (Cowboys) Rilee Jorgensen (Titans) Annessa Biddle wins the award! She's not here either unfortunately. "I'm just so honoured and privileged to win this award," she says. She thanks her family: "It hit different being away from home," she says.
